# BUG-005 Header Text Overlaps Image
## Environment
- Mobile
## Severity

Medium

## Priority

Medium

## Preconditions

Website homepage is accessible on mobile device.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open homepage on mobile device
2. Observe header/banner section
## Expected Result

Header text should be properly aligned and fully readable without overlapping visual elements.

## Actual Result

Header text overlaps the image and reduces readability.

## Status

Open
